!!`<<thvSelectAll>>`
Where to use: `tbl-th-view`

<<<
Displays a checkbox which, if flagged, marks ''all of the table rows'' as selected. Selected rows are affected by actions triggered by "//Edit selected//" and "//Delete selected//" in the control toolbar (it is a chance to delete all of the rows).
<<<

